CREATE VIEW [business_rules].[component_s_dbt_rule_c_factcomponent]
AS

  SELECT 
    bo.[business key for hub component],    -- Business Key for Hub Component
    bo.[tcases],                            -- [tcases] from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics Calculation
    bo.[creqs],                             -- [creqs] from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics Calculation
    bo.[creqswithtracetotcase],             -- [creqswithtracetotcase] from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics Calculation
    bo.[tcase_pro_creq],                    -- [tcase_pro_creq] from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics Calculation
    bo.[minpth],                            -- [minpth] from Satellite Component > DBT_STAGE > Test Metric PTH
    bo.[maxpth],                            -- [maxpth] from Satellite Component > DBT_STAGE > Test Metric PTH
    bo.[implpth]                            -- [implpth] from Satellite Component > DBT_STAGE > Test Metric PTH

  FROM [businessobjects].[component_s_dbt_rule_c_factcomponent] AS bo
;
